# Licensed timer font — NOT redistributed here (commercial TT Norms derivative).
# Place your own copy at MacTimeTracker/Resources/Fonts/ to build with the real
# face; without it the app falls back to the rounded system font. See README.
MacTimeTracker/Resources/Fonts/*.ttf
MacTimeTracker/Resources/Fonts/*.otf
MacTimeTracker/Resources/Fonts/*.ttc
